ore":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-07-06T15:45:38.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>邊度換牌抵</blockquote><br />\n間間差唔多"},{"pid":"805453b961314ce20848ca915e860c3898e18652","tid":306432,"uid":48762,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-07-06T15:47:25.000Z","msg":"<blockquote><blockquote>去我鄉下玩<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n巴打住巽寮灣個頭？<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/hehe.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n我係巽寮灣個頭"},{"pid":"71f99497e53419c5fb18125f7fad9bb639ed8482","tid":306432,"uid":52215,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-07-07T02:16:40.000Z","msg":"<blockquote><blockquote><blockquote>去我鄉下玩<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n巴打住巽寮灣個頭？<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/hehe.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n我係巽寮灣個頭</blockquote><br />\n雙月灣個面？？"},{"pid":"3a8da92fd760b008719d93ce8ec0e5d2cae2b91e","tid":306432,"uid":44171,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-07-07T02:29:33.000Z","msg":"<blockquote><blockquote><blockquote><blockquote>去我鄉下玩<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n巴打住巽寮灣個頭？<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/hehe.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n我係巽寮灣個頭</blockquote><br />\n雙月灣個面？？</blockquote><br />\n巽寮係高速入口果頭, 金融街果邊"},{"pid":"026a7b35a4c9c67b83539abcdab74a46fc6b9fbe","tid":306432,"uid":84933,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-07-07T03:43:16.000Z","msg":"<blockquote><blockquote><blockquote><img src=\"https://holland.pk/lujq2fn1\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fholland.pk%2Flujq2fn1&h=983bdc35&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n上個禮拜先去完 <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/bye.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n巴打住邊間洒店，好靚<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/tongue.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n住萬科果邊最好, 水最靚, 你去遲左5年, 以前D水清到見底, D魚手掌咁大條係你腳邊游黎游去, 仲可以渣車係沙灘飛車, 家下D水已經唔清, 魚又無晒, 仲有唔好出海玩果D捕漁之類, D魚本地人都唔敢食.<br />\n<br />\n家下惠東都好貴, D水越黎越差, 北面D水仲污染, 雙月灣另一面D水又黑又臭, 又車多人多, 海邊仲可以去西面陽江果邊, 4個鐘左右, D水先叫靚, 再遠真係要去到廣西先得, 海鮮真係平到笑, 成檯海鮮都係2,3百 <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/tongue.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n<br />\n我屋企人講二十幾三十年前，惠東既水質係好好，我個時問有冇個d旅遊特輯咁靚，水清沙幼，佢地話有<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/shocking.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n依家個d臭水有汽油味，真係咪搞<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"fa62da1136bc65500018497034b3323cdc2e646b","tid":306432,"uid":52215,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-07-07T09:00:24.000Z","msg":"<blockquote><blockquote><blockquote><blockquote><img src=\"https://holland.pk/lujq2fn1\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fholland.pk%2Flujq2fn1&h=983bdc35&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n上個禮拜先去完 <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/bye.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n巴打住邊間洒店，好靚<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/tongue.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n住萬科果邊最好, 水最靚, 你去遲左5年, 以前D水清到見底, D魚手掌咁大條係你腳邊游黎游去, 仲可以渣車係沙灘飛車, 家下D水已經唔清, 魚又無晒, 仲有唔好出海玩果D捕漁之類, D魚本地人都唔敢食.<br />\n<br />\n家下惠東都好貴, D水越黎越差, 北面D水仲污染, 雙月灣另一面D水又黑又臭, 又車多人多, 海邊仲可以去西面陽江果邊, 4個鐘左右, D水先叫靚, 再遠真係要去到廣西先得, 海鮮真係平到笑, 成檯海鮮都係2,3百 <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/tongue.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n<br />\n我屋企人講二十幾三十年前，惠東既水質係好好，我個時問有冇個d旅遊特輯咁靚，水清沙幼，佢地話有<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/shocking.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n依家個d臭水有汽油味，真係咪搞<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"0d6b0ed6352c8d39e927bf5891ea7a39528a632b","tid":306432,"uid":42629,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-07-08T19:50:18.000Z","msg":"想租S90<br />\n<a href=\"https://order.zuche.com/cardetail-843?t=0\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Forder.zuche.com%2Fcardetail-843%3Ft%3D0&d=9yoZYS%2FQykZn281u0QSjpDOU%2Fspzl0GStOx2S