src=\"/assets/faces/normal/kill.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n <img src=\"/assets/faces/lomoji/05.png\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> 一樣 清明覺得係大件事 重要過新年</blockquote><br />\n年年清明返去,塞車都塞到暈,啲路又窄,車又多,遲早收皮</blockquote><br />\n我係雙月灣出番黎巽寮灣，有條村路窄到仆街，車又多，痴撚線<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"}]}